item.title: How Chat GPT is Changing the Game
item.description: Chat GPT is a natural language processing tool that helps chatbots generate human-like text. Based on the advanced GPT-3 model, Chat GPT allows for more natural and engaging conversations in real-time. It is widely used in customer service chatbots, virtual assistants, and conversational AI platforms.
